{"tid":1632344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蒙面法例第一控 兩男女今天東區法院提堂","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:46:50.000Z","uid":234352,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e3126c86298b2d1eac65b431bae41760f70e9fc9","tid":1632344,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"蒙面法例第一控 兩男女今天東區法院提堂<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191007&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60125390\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191007%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60125390&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=e196ab06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191007%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60125390&h=0c867001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191007&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60125390</a><br />\n<br />\n本港實施蒙面法後，兩名男女首度因蒙面而遭檢控，警方表示，在10月5日凌晨，於觀塘啟田道發現有人非法集結及用雜物設置路障，企圖堵塞馬路。警員於現場拘捕一名18歲男子及一名38歲女子。該兩名男女已被暫控合共一項非法集結及各一項違反《禁止蒙面規例》」罪。案件今日於東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁撚快就提堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fef2e5cfe84f302f47b149a0f84e2c7fd6c7e8","tid":1632344,"uid":270629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」繞過立法會直接立法，公然破壞香港法治制度。<br />\n三罷公投，投票表達意向！<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一